{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f1b9672a91","title":"膜点问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ac1be9dc14","index":0,"year":1964,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"f1b9672a91"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f43d12c609","type":"title","text":"赠点问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f1b9672a91"},{"id":"133e970c4e","type":"paragraph","text":"革命失败后的一段时间，调查没有研究，实在气得要死。红军到一个地方，屁股坐不住，吃了就走，当时林彪同志说要有“灵活战术”，大家反对说这叫新花样，“步兵操典上没讲，步兵操典是人家经过流血写出来的，搞什么新花样”。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f1b9672a91"},{"id":"dd5a593ffb","type":"paragraph","text":"膜点不膜点，不知道什么叫工业，一不请教工人，二不请教技术人员，这怎么行？不了解情况，为什么不学？应该懂些嘛。搞了几年了，恐怕就是不膜点，毫不知道。可以到白银厂学习，没有到工厂学习，不向工人学习，不向技术人员请教，总是内心无主。踏点也要采取比较法，比学赶帮，首先是比较法嘛，马克思主义和修正主义也是比较嘛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f1b9672a91"}],"page":{"id":"6dd43090ef","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f1b9672a91","start":396,"end":396}}}},"__N_SSG":true}